<EventList>

<!-- Introduction avec le souffleur -->
<event id="Introduction">

    <musique name="Commedia Theme Redux" disappearTime="1" waitTime="0" appearTime="5" repeat="1" reset="true"/>
	<musique name="Theme Tuto" disappearTime="1" waitTime="50"  appearTime="1" repeat="-1"/>
	
	<guiManager active="false"/>
	
	<character name="Arlequin">
		<deplacement x="-16.7" y="-2.2" z="0" instant="true"/>
	</character>
	
	<wait time="0.2"/>
	
	<character name="Arlequin">
		<deplacement x="-16" y="7" z="30"/>
		<sound name="1_entree" wait="false" volume="0.7" />
	</character>
	
	<wait time="1"/>
	
	<camera>
			<deplacement x="-0.6" y="20" z="15.5" wait="false"/>	
	</camera>
		
	<souffleur position="milieu">
		<sound name="1_salut" wait ="false"/>
		<talk>
			<paragraph>Welcome, dear actor ! As you are new to our company, I am going to guide you. So listen to me carefully !</paragraph>
			<paragraph>Your role is &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;Arlecchino&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62;, a famous character from Italy. You represent the people and they like you for your mocking manners, your intelligence and your trickery.</paragraph>
			<paragraph>You are still a beginner in this essential role, but I'm quite sure you'll do much better than your predecessor. Follow my advice and you'll be the people's favorite !</paragraph>
		</talk>
	</souffleur>
	
	<camera>
			<reset wait="false"/>	
	</camera>
	
	<multiple>
		<camera>
			<deplacement x="0" y="6" z="0" wait="false"/>	
		</camera>
		<public><addvalue value="20"/></public>
		<souffleur position="gauche">
		<talk>
			<paragraph>Come on, now you have to entertain those good people to gather maximum audience. We are &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;touring actors&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62; : we have to play each day to earn our living.</paragraph>
			<paragraph>If we do well, it is possible to be given &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;food, drinks&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62; and even &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;a place to sleep for the night&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62; ! (It's still better than being forced to &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;sleep hungry&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62; in a caravan, isn't it ?)</paragraph>
		</talk>
	</souffleur>
	</multiple>
	
	<camera>
			<reset wait="false"/>	
	</camera>
	<wait time="0.5"/>

	
	<multiple>
		<souffleur position="droite">
			<talk>
				<paragraph>You see that trunk on the right ? &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;Search inside&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62; to see if a &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;prop&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62; cannot help you to catch the eye of the passersby.</paragraph>
			</talk>
		</souffleur>		
		<camera>
				<deplacement x="17" y="10" z="16" wait="false"/>	
		</camera>
	</multiple>
	
	<camera>
			<reset wait="false"/>	
	</camera>
	
	<guiManager active="true"/>
</event>

<!-- Arrivée du capitaine -->
<event id="Tutorial_2">
	<guiManager active="false"/>
	
	<character name="Capitaine">
		<deplacement x="-16.7" y="-2.2" z="-10.5" instant="true"/>
		<deplacement x="-16.7" y="-2.2" z="23.32" />
	</character>
	
	<camera>
		<deplacement x="-9.89" y="13.57" z="4.27" wait="false"/>	
	</camera>
		
	<character name="Capitaine">
		<deplacement x="-16" y="7" z="30"/>
		<sound name="1_entree" wait="false" volume="0.5" />
	</character>
	<wait time="0.5"/>
	<multiple>
		<character name="Capitaine">
			<sound name="2_ignore" wait="false" volume="0.5" />		    
			<animation name="moquerie"/>
		</character>
		<souffleur position="gauche">
			<talk>
				<paragraph>This character is the &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;Capitano&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62;. It's a soldier. He seems intimidating at first, but in reality &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;it's a coward who's affraid of his own shadow&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62;.</paragraph>
				<paragraph>Giving a good lesson to this swaggerer will attract you the favors of our first audience !</paragraph>
				<paragraph>But I have faith in you, kiddo ! If you accompish &#60;b&#62;&#60;color=#0054ff&#62;several actions to scare him off&#60;/color&#62;&#60;/b&#62;, he will go cry into his mother's skirt ! It's up to you now ! </paragraph>
			</talk>
		</souffleur>
	</multiple>	
	
	<camera>
			<reset wait="false"/>	
	</camera>
	
	<character name="Capitaine">
		<interaction value="true"/>
	</character>
	
	<guiManager active="true"/>
</event>

